2" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='t$t$19793502'><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-1003bb2fb402f1b21f60b7d5ca555b71_l.jpg" alt="知乎圆桌" class="avatar d50"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/topic/19793502" class="name" data-hovercard='t$t$19793502'>知乎圆桌</a><div class="bio">举办过 253 场圆桌</div></div></div><div class="item-body"><p class="description">知乎发起的在线嘉宾讨论，详情请点击：<a href="http://www.zhihu.com/question/20886632" data-editable="true" data-title="什么是「知乎圆桌」？如何参与" class="">什么是「知乎圆桌」？如何参与</a>？<br>圆桌页面：<a href="http://www.zhihu.com/roundtable" data-editable="true" data-title="活动">活动列表</a></p></div></li></ul></div></div><div class="module guests"><div class="module-header"><h3>嘉宾</h3></div><div class="module-body"><ul class="items"><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/yi-han-40-51" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$yi-han-40-51'><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/07d9fbcf1a1ea7a0ea51ca72aa1a0a9e_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="朱骏超律师"></img></a><div class="content"><a class="name author-link" href="/people/yi-han-40-51" data-hovercard='p$t$yi-han-40-51'>朱骏超律师</a><div class="bio">诺诚游戏法创始人、游戏行业律师</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/shang-long-91" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$shang-long-91'><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-1a66da973693866c4423a3afdf7f7944_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="周俊武"></img></a><div class="content"><a class="name author-link" href="/people/shang-long-91" data-hovercard='p$t$shang-long-91'>周俊武</a><div class="bio">法律界最知娱乐  娱乐圈最懂法律</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/wang-a-53-16" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$wang-a-53-16'><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-00c2ba83f22e697e7f7588ade3d70e27_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="汪超男律师"></img></a><div class="content"><a class="name author-link" href="/people/wang-a-53-16" data-hovercard='p$t$wang-a-53-16'>汪超男律师</a><span c